README for pp/src/foundry
====== === ==============

CONTENTS
========

This directory contains the ProofPower fonts

The ProofPower fonts are derived from the GNU FreeFont fonts
and are distributed as part of OpenProofPower. The ProofPower
fonts were incorporated in the OpenProofPower source
on 9th September 2018.

